    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable, functional option for anyone looking for a solid driver at an accessible price point. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, small dents, and fading paint in a few spots. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear and the cabin has some signs of use, though all essential electronics and climate controls remain operational. Mechanically, it runs well and has been regularly serviced, though it may require some minor maintenance in the near future. It\u2019s a dependable car that gets the job done without the premium price tag of a newer model.",
