      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty car! It\u2019s been so reliable and is still in really solid shape\u2014perfect for someone who wants a quality ride without the brand-new price tag. It runs beautifully and has been well-loved. I\u2019m super easy to work with and would love to see this go to a great owner, so feel free to reach out with any questions. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
