      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a linear power delivery peaking at an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis has been enhanced with poly-bushing upgrades and a reinforced rear subframe to mitigate common structural fatigue. Recent mechanical highlights include a comprehensive Vanos overhaul and a precise valve adjustment, ensuring the valvetrain operates with factory-spec urgency. It is a mechanically robust example of the ultimate driving machine, optimized for tactile feedback and balanced handling.",
